# Cloudflare Pages SPA fallback — every non-asset path falls through to
# index.html so React Router takes over client-side. Without this, a hard
# reload on /expense / /wish / etc. would 404. Vite copies anything in
# public/ into the dist root at build time, so this file lands at /dist/
# /_redirects exactly where Pages expects it.
/*    /index.html   200
